body_html:
Those packages (https://github.com/samjabrahams/tensorflow-on-raspberry-pi and https://github.com/tflearn/tflearn.git) are not produced by the maintainers of the TensorFlow repository and are not part of the official release.

Since this isn't something owned or maintained by the TensorFlow maintainers, I'm going to close this out. I'd recommend building from source (perhaps using the instructions from @samjabrahams )
